      "title": "One shot and killed a house intruder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A person has died in a shooting that took place in a house yesterday (27) night in Rathmalanai - Silva Mawatha area under Kalgisai Police Division.",
        "The police said that the person who was seriously injured in the shooting died after being admitted to a hospital in Kalupovila.",
        "A 30-year-old tricycle driver from the same area died in the incident."
      ],
